1. *Otvorim* oči (I opened my eyes).
2. On je *otvorio* vrata (He opened the door).
3. *Otvori* joj vrata (Open the door for her).
4. *Otvaram* vrata (I'm opening the door).
5. Odlučio je *otvoriti* situaciju (He decided to open the situation).
6. *Otvori* mi knjigu (Open the book for me).
7. *Otvarala* su se vrata (The doors were being opened).
8. Ona je *otvorila* njegovu knjigu (She opened his book).